data.description: Welcome to your new home at 3722 SW 88th PL in the heart of Miami, Florida. This charming residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, this single-family home features 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and 918 square feet of living space.     Located in a family-friendly community, this property is within close proximity to restaurants and shopping centers. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways such as the Palmetto and thoroughfares, connecting you to all that Miami has to offer.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 3722 SW 88th PL your new address. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and lifestyle this home has to offer.
